    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Line Clipper: Tennis Tactics》是一款回合制战术网球游戏。你需要洞察对手的比赛套路，掌握球场主动权。每次出手前，你都可以规划完美球路并模拟击球结果。赛场形势瞬息万变，有时你可以畅快出击，有时你只能打出压线一球。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/7709fde6e748a8a04a312375fda69d0b.poster.avif?t=1762491672\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/7709fde6e748a8a04a312375fda69d0b.webm?t=1762491672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/7709fde6e748a8a04a312375fda69d0b.mp4?t=1762491672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >打造自己的击球风格：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精心调整战略，塑造专属击球风格，构建独家思路轻松拿分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/2ef24e9e893df7173b79c9757e693351.poster.avif?t=1762491672\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/2ef24e9e893df7173b79c9757e693351.webm?t=1762491672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/2ef24e9e893df7173b79c9757e693351.mp4?t=1762491672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >得分回合详解：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每分共有四个阶段，并依此循环：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >1. 瞄球：调整击球落点、力度和旋转类型，迫使对手陷入被动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2. 回位：趁对手全神贯注、预备击球时，迅速返回球场中心或摸向网前。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >3. 预判与备击：预判对手球路，做好击球准备。精准预判并坚持既定战术，即可提高击球准确度。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4. 跑位击球：综合考虑站位、球高、球速等多种因素，选择最佳击球点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/a41cc5226205ecedf3acaba2dc331f68.poster.avif?t=1762491672\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/a41cc5226205ecedf3acaba2dc331f68.webm?t=1762491672\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3205410/extras/a41cc5226205ecedf3acaba2dc331f68.mp4?t=1762491672\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >生涯模式：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是专注提升世界排名，还是全身心投入顶级赛事？加入生涯模式，由你来规划自己的职业发展方向。</p>",
